This site includes FRC Team 4159 CardinalBotics' project documentation, references, and blog on FRC software, controls, and electronics.

Our mission is to preserve and pass down knowledge to future generation of Cardinals. Most of the content will be references to other people/team's works, to save the time and repetition of writing all these tutorials ourselves.

This website is still under construction.
